Installation
============

git clone git@github.com:blazingcloud/driveless-repo.git
Create gemset: 1.8.7@driveless
bundle install
copy database.sample-mac.yml to database.yml and edit per your environment
rake db:create
rake db:migrate
rake db:seed
rake spec
script/server
